      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Sisters Sally Forth",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "There\u0027s been reports of three\r\nmonsters wreaking havoc out\r\nin the Frost Islands. Rondine\r\nand I are being dispatched to\r\nresolve the issue. If you would\r\njoin, surely the three of us can\r\nmake quick work of them.",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Les s\u0153urs \u00E0 l\u0027attaque",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Trois monstres feraient des\r\nravages \u00E0 l\u0027Archipel de glace.\r\nRondine et moi avons \u00E9t\u00E9\r\ncharg\u00E9es de nous occuper\r\nd\u0027eux. Tu veux nous aider ?\r\nJe suis s\u00FBre qu\u0027on ira plus\r\nvite tous les trois.",
        "Target": "Chasser tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Avanti, sorelle!",
        "Client": "Dama Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Sembra che tre mostri stiano\r\nseminando il caos alle Isole\r\nghiacciate. Io e Rondine\r\nveniamo inviate a sistemare il\r\nproblema. Vuoi venire con noi?\r\nIn tre faremo in un attimo.",
        "Target": "Caccia tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Vorw\u00E4rts, Schwestern!",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Drei Monster richten auf den\r\nFrostinseln gro\u00DFen Schaden an.\r\nRondine und ich werden losge-\r\nschickt, um das Problem zu l\u00F6sen.\r\nWenn du mitmachen w\u00FCrdest,\r\nk\u00F6nnten wir drei sicher schnell\r\nmit ihnen fertig werden.",
        "Target": "Erjage alle Zielmonster.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Expedici\u00F3n con las hermanas",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Me informan que tres monstruos\r\nest\u00E1n sembrando el caos en las\r\nIslas heladas. Nos han pedido\r\na Rondine y a m\u00ED que actuemos\r\nsin demora. \u00BFQuieres venir con\r\nnosotras? S\u00E9 que \u003CLSNR {juntos} {juntas}\u003E lo\r\nsolucionaremos en poco tiempo.",
        "Target": "Caza todos los objetivos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
